</p><a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/" target="_blank" data-pf-type="Button2" class="sc-hOGkXu gCnidx pf-158_ pf-button-1">Explore here.</a></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-24ce" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-uojGG hMqLeX pf-160_ pf-color-scheme-1 pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-ilfuhL bpQaoh"><div class="sc-iqseJM ducrfW pf-161_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-162_"><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-163_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">In today's rapidly changing world, traditional learning methods often fall short in equipping individuals and organisations with the skills needed to thrive. Enter agile learning - a dynamic approach emphasising adaptability, collaboration, and continuous improvement. In this blog, we'll explore the concept of agile learning, its benefits in engaging learners, and highlight key organisations offering support and resources in this transformative journey, including The Mandatory Training Group, a leading UK provider of agile learning content.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-iqseJM ducrfW pf-165_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-166_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bTfYFJ fFWOZc pf-167_ pf-heading-1-h3">What is agile learning?
</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/2_ff742440-fcf2-407a-b1b4-c200d88eba84.png?v=1709045106" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/2_ff742440-fcf2-407a-b1b4-c200d88eba84.png?v=1709045106 1536w" width="1408" height="1056" alt="2.png__PID:9008ff5d-47d5-46d4-8034-2cf3f83109d4" title="Unlocking Potential: Exploring Interactive Learning Solutions - The Mandatory Training Group UK - " data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-169_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-170_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by Azrin90 via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-172_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Agile is an iterative approach to project management and software development that prioritises flexibility, collaboration, and customer feedback. It emphasises adaptive planning, continuous improvement, and delivering value incrementally in short iterations. Agile methodologies, such as Scrum and Kanban, enable teams to respond quickly to changing requirements and deliver high-quality products efficiently.<br><br>At its core, agile learning is about fostering a culture of adaptability and innovation in education and professional development. It involves:
<br>
</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-kYHfwS lkFAWj pf-174_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-175_ pf-text-1"><b>Adaptability</b> - Quickly responding to changing needs and circumstances.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-177_ pf-text-1"><b>Collaboration</b> - Emphasising teamwork and peer-to-peer learning.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-179_ pf-text-1"><b>Iteration</b> - Continuously refining learning experiences based on feedback.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-181_ pf-text-1"><b>Flexibility</b> - Offering a variety of learning formats and pathways.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-183_ pf-text-1"><b>Technology integration</b> - Leveraging digital tools for enhanced learning experiences.
</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-iqseJM ducrfW pf-185_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-186_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bTfYFJ fFWOZc pf-187_ pf-heading-1-h3">Background, key facts, and statistics
</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/3_3d527365-e6e0-4ae8-8fef-e7dbba0f7ff3.png?v=1709045105" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/3_3d527365-e6e0-4ae8-8fef-e7dbba0f7ff3.png?v=1709045105 1536w" width="1419" height="946" alt="3.png__PID:08ff5d47-d516-4440-b42c-f3f83109d406" title="Revolutionise Training with Interactive Learning Platforms - The Mandatory Training Group UK - " data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-189_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-190_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by mohdizzuanbinroslan via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-192_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Agile learning is a mindset and methodology borrowed from the world of software development, where it originated as a response to the limitations of rigid, waterfall-style project management. 
</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-kYHfwS lkFAWj pf-194_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-195_ pf-text-1">According to a report by the Association for Talent Development (ATD), 83% of organisations say that agile approaches are used in some form within their organisation for learning and development.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-197_ pf-text-1">61% of companies use agile to achieve both software development and company-wide digital transformation
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-199_ pf-text-1">Agile success rate remains at the 80th percentile, as compared to other models
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-201_ pf-text-1">The agile approach offered 40% improved project transparency across different departments of the surveyed organisations.
</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-iqseJM ducrfW pf-203_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-204_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bTfYFJ fFWOZc pf-205_ pf-heading-1-h3">Agile learning culture
</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/4_a9af98cf-68af-4282-a294-01bf8a19921b.png?v=1709045106" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/4_a9af98cf-68af-4282-a294-01bf8a19921b.png?v=1709045106 1536w" width="1286" height="858" alt="4.png__PID:ff5d47d5-16d4-4034-acf3-f83109d40635" title="Master Skills with Cutting-Edge Interactive Learning Courses - The Mandatory Training Group UK - " data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-207_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-208_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by monkeybusiness via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-210_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">An agile learning culture refers to an organisational environment that fosters adaptability, collaboration, and continuous improvement in learning and development practices.
</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-kYHfwS lkFAWj pf-212_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-213_ pf-text-1"><b></b><second-sel><b>Adaptability</b></second-sel><b></b> - The organisation is responsive to change, quickly adjusting learning strategies, content, and delivery methods to meet evolving needs and circumstances.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-215_ pf-text-1"><b>Collaboration</b> - There is a strong emphasis on teamwork and knowledge sharing among learners, instructors, and other stakeholders.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-217_ pf-text-1"><b>Continuous improvement </b>- Learning experiences are continually evaluated and refined based on feedback and results.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-219_ pf-text-1"><b>Flexibility</b> - The organisation offers diverse learning formats and pathways to accommodate the individual needs and preferences of learners.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-221_ pf-text-1"><b>Empowerment </b>- Learners are encouraged to take ownership of their learning journey and pursue opportunities for growth and development.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-223_ pf-text-1"><b>Experimentation</b> - There is a culture of experimentation and risk-taking, where learners are encouraged to try new approaches and learn from both successes and failures.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-225_ pf-text-1"><b>Technology Integration </b>- Digital tools and technology are leveraged to enhance learning experiences and facilitate collaboration, communication, and access to resources.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-iqseJM ducrfW pf-227_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-228_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bTfYFJ fFWOZc pf-229_ pf-heading-1-h3">Adaptability in action
</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/5_0c023fc8-20d9-414d-976a-70f28f6ced6b.png?v=1709045106" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/5_0c023fc8-20d9-414d-976a-70f28f6ced6b.png?v=1709045106 1536w" width="1792" height="1344" alt="5.png__PID:5d47d516-d440-442c-b3f8-3109d406355c" title="Interactive Training Programs: Engaging, Effective, Empowering - The Mandatory Training Group UK - " data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-231_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-232_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by wanaktek via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-234_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Agile learning enables educators and trainers to pivot quickly in response to learner feedback and changing industry demands. By embracing agile principles, institutions can develop courses and programs that remain relevant and impactful in the face of rapid change.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-iqseJM ducrfW pf-236_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-237_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bTfYFJ fFWOZc pf-238_ pf-heading-1-h3">Collaboration for success
</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/6_96eb9901-7aed-4eaa-ae9d-0838fdc17695.png?v=1709053410" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/6_96eb9901-7aed-4eaa-ae9d-0838fdc17695.png?v=1709053410 1536w" width="1981" height="1321" alt="6.png__PID:c59f806a-75bd-4c48-ac56-3fa565a5eebc" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-240_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-241_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by Raul_Mellado via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-243_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Through collaborative projects and group activities, agile learning fosters a sense of community and teamwork among learners. By working together to solve problems and share knowledge, individuals not only deepen their understanding but also develop essential communication and interpersonal skills.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-iqseJM ducrfW pf-245_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-246_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bTfYFJ fFWOZc pf-247_ pf-heading-1-h3">Iterative improvement
